# MarsCodingExercise
1 . Here I used IN-memory DB - H2..  

2. Application will accept both XML and JSON request from POSTMAN.

 postman urls :
 
 save -> http://localhost:8080/mars/addPerson
 getPersons -> http://localhost:8080/mars/getPersons
 editPerson -> http://localhost:8080/mars/editPerson
 deletePerson->http://localhost:8080/mars/deletePerson/1
  getCount -> http://localhost:8080/mars/getCount

3. Sample User save request

	<item>
        <firstName>Vallesh</firstName>
        <surName>Venkannagari</surName>
    </item>
